1
00:01:29,549 --> 00:01:30,634
Shave him bald.

2
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:44,928
You're lucky to get a free haircut.

3
00:01:52,570 --> 00:01:55,068
Whose are you, little one? Eh?

4
00:01:58,055 --> 00:02:06,936
A Strip of Uncut Wild Flowers

5
00:02:14,026 --> 00:02:15,100
Who is your father?

6
00:02:15,812 --> 00:02:20,428
Nobody. I was brought
by the wind, ownerless.

7
00:02:20,552 --> 00:02:23,621
Written by Oles Gonchar & Yuri Ilyenko
from novel "Brigantina" by O. Gonchar

8
